{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2943373, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "居然这么多人觉得学生真应该非必要不出校", "timestamp": 1636949138, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943391, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "海淀有病例的情况下，非要去病例所在地附近吃饭，是很对周围人负责人的做法？\n", "timestamp": 1636949269, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943423, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943391, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 可以是次密接和密接一起在校外吃饭啊", "timestamp": 1636949513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943431, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943423, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 那这种情况不该被指责呀，但是这和“非不要不出校”不矛盾，一级密接者里还是有人刻意违反了的", "timestamp": 1636949588, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943433, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943423, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 比如去上地吃海底捞，我不太能想到其必要的理由", "timestamp": 1636949607, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943453, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943433, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 你指现在去上地海底捞吃饭还是之前，之前去吃的怎么能提前预料到会出事。", "timestamp": 1636949728, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943462, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "人得讲道理，自己出校报备审批都过了，最后成为密接？你处分我的原因是不必要？？？人得讲理啊，又不是人家想成为密接的", "timestamp": 1636949770, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943472, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943453, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我如果没记错 北京上一次中关村那附近确诊之后 就该收严了吧，还没过十四天（11.2海底捞这次）大多数同学肯定不会故意找麻烦，但现在即便是海淀区6个确诊，也有大把同学到处乱跑乱玩，还有密接了还参加各种活动的……", "timestamp": 1636949885, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943475, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我感觉主要看时间顺序，如果明知道自己有时空交集只是暂时没成为密接，依然选择出去聚餐是有问题。", "timestamp": 1636949937, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943477, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943472, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 密接这个统计早就有了，在昨天大批隔离之前，所以并不是开始隔离才统计的密接", "timestamp": 1636949961, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943482, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943475, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 昨天两大批，其中一批就是有个人明知有重叠，还参加各种聚集性活动，所以抓了一票人", "timestamp": 1636949997, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943494, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943472, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我咋没懂呢，海淀区6个确诊跟我去五道口吃饭有啥关系。", "timestamp": 1636950141, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943503, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果我自己在学校里待着，哪里都不去，而室友到处乱跑导致我受影响，还是免不了对室友有意见（", "timestamp": 1636950245, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943505, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943494, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 很容易密接，在流调完全出来之前，我个人感觉无论是对自己安全还是对他人安全考虑，这几天可以先忍忍", "timestamp": 1636950255, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943507, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943453, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 如果是明知，就不行", "timestamp": 1636950266, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943581, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": 2943505, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 6个确诊的流调不是早就出来了？还有新的？", "timestamp": 1636950815, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2943616, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 559193, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "至少我是不敢出校，目前海淀这情况没有说完全确认没有传染链吧", "timestamp": 1636951066, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 559193, "reply": 17, "tag": null, "text": "如果室友正常出校吃饭导致我三级密接被隔离，我只会喷政策喷运气不好，不会对室友有任何意见。围观了一下树洞不会只有我是这样吧。", "timestamp": 1636949107, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1636951065, "url": "", "vote": {}}}